children.subject: Thank you! However, I feel as though not taking 170 next semester would put me at a disadvantage for interviews/potential internships I want to apply for next school year, which is why I am conflicted.

They are each 5% of your class grade.
Does babak still do that thing where he passes a microphone to a random student to answer a question? I remember that happened a lot in 16A

I have not taken 170, but can speak to 120 - it's a very useful class for other EE upper divs, and has a fairly light workload. Babak is teaching it this fall and he's excellent. Highly recommend the class and consider it a good complement to 61C (I took 61C, 120, and 149 last semester).
